{"tid":378154,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 69歲汪呀姐演唱會嬌俏扮鬼新娘 與嫩男Dancer 舞台上拜堂咀咀","createTime":"2017-08-28T09:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T08:13:34.000Z","uid":22349,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb5dfe66b85f846f51c16e7693ff00820dc777c2","tid":378154,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"絕色嬌俏女鬼汪阿蛆，猶如聶小倩再世。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/164859_20c60efb679c8b5380ff2a1fb30939b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F164859_20c60efb679c8b5380ff2a1fb30939b6.jpg&h=80757e84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/164859_2edc1e5e1e0a538821a3123bef54320e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F164859_2edc1e5e1e0a538821a3123bef54320e.jpg&h=0976110f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">她的眼光，她的眼光，好似好似星星發光<br />\n睇見，睇見，睇見，睇見，心慌慌</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女鬼汪呀蛆 受汪老妖所迫，需引誘男子，與其親熱時殺害，以血供奉黑山姥姥。下圖為千年汪老妖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/165903_e1e823812d3a01eeb672e83766018a18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F165903_e1e823812d3a01eeb672e83766018a18.jpg&h=00eb299a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入世未深既男Dancer 巧遇女鬼汪阿姐。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/165936_e179f2a0f88d1fd7d7820b232aa32172.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F165936_e179f2a0f88d1fd7d7820b232aa32172.jpg&h=dc34e26c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>明月吐光，冤鬼風裡蕩，夜更深霧更寒<br />\n遊魂踏遍，幽寂路上</strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女鬼以豔舞和黃金多番挑逗男Dancer。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/170008_2b9022ec1d4520e9695ca0665ec625dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F170008_2b9022ec1d4520e9695ca0665ec625dc.jpg&h=f63b9cda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/170009_4a60ed527e5e1cd69f311adce0f50bb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F170009_4a60ed527e5e1cd69f311adce0f50bb7.jpg&h=3fdf5e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">天際朗月也不願看，天際朗月也不願看<br />\n明月吐光，陰風吹柳巷，是女鬼覓愛郎<br />\n誰人願愛，淒厲鬼新娘</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為左天下蒼生 眼睛同耳朵既健康，男Dancer 憤然決定迎娶女鬼汪呀蛆，兩人就係咁譜出一段可歌可泣既愛情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/165041_852e7c5dba4333a2db2fdfe18a7d84f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F165041_852e7c5dba4333a2db2fdfe18a7d84f0.jpg&h=259784ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/165042_852e7c5dba4333a2db2fdfe18a7d84f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F165042_852e7c5dba4333a2db2fdfe18a7d84f0.jpg&h=c6de3309&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/165042_ba046298b1c6b9f2191dfae4e3361046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F165042_ba046298b1c6b9f2191dfae4e3361046.jpg&h=7dc190d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/165043_ba046298b1c6b9f2191dfae4e3361046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F165043_ba046298b1c6b9f2191dfae4e3361046.jpg&h=95d60078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/165043_2ca1cb78d6a930579191b272df964b83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https